Business Brief -- Lewis Galoob Toys Inc.:
   Toy Maker Sues Spencer
   Over Sale of Game Modifier
The alleged improper sales had no serious financial impact
on Galoob, a spokesman said, but the South San Francisco,
Calif., company was seeking an injunction and damages to be
determined later. "We are dismayed that this major American
retailer would circumvent legal distribution channels," he
said.
   Spencer could not be reached for comment.